{
  "texts": [
    "The figure on the horizontal axis has the timeline, while on the vertical axis the impact of the work (measured as citations) on a logarithmic scale.",
    "The horizontal texts denote the articles, while the vertical texts include the most relevant connections to the corresponding article.",
    "The color encoding is related to the domain, i.e.",
    "the data type which is accepted at the input of the methods.",
    "As a period, we considered in the reference the work of Kingma and Welling (2014) from 2014 till today covering more than a decade of VAE-based spatial data processing methods."
  ]
